This basic salvage tool never runs out of charges. It can break an unlimited number of items down into their base components.

Change your backpack to this custom skin. Usable as a back-slot item for any character.

Play colorful Super Adventure Box tunes in-game on this permanent music box. All tunes are pre-recorded. No musical skill required!
